.\" Manpage for the ardu-serial library
.\" Author: Sebastian Jordan <sebastian.jordan.mail@googlemail.com>
.TH ARDU-LIB 3 "18 Novembre 2013" "1.0" "ardu-serial man page"
.SH NAME 
ardu-serial \- Library to access serial communication with an arduino board
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include <ardu-serial.h>
.sp
.BI "int ser_init(char *" device ", int " BaudRate ");"
.BI "int ser_getc(int " file ", char *" readCharacter ");"
.BI "int ser_flush(int " file ");"
.BI "int ser_readln(int " file ", char *" buffer ");"
.BI "int ser_putc(int " file ", char " character ");"
.BI "int ser_println(int " file ", char *" buffer ");"
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B ardu-serial
library offers methods to communitcate the a arduino board
mounted to a computer via a serial connection.